data.description: Enjoy many upgrades, modern amenities and exceptional classic design in this beautiful home! Fall in love with the beautiful interior, perfectly crafted to accommodate your lifestyle. As you enter the home you are greeted with hardwood floors, tall ceilings and lots of natural light.  Entertain guests in the living room and wine and dine guests in the dining room open to the kitchen.  The kitchen is spacious with tile flooring, tons of cabinets and prep space and updated appliances.  There is a powder room next to the kitchen for added convenience. Upstairs you will find a large primary suite with hardwood floors, walk in closet and an ensuite bathroom with tile floors and a stand up shower.  There are two additional bedrooms and a shared hall bathroom with a tile surround tub/shower combo.  The lower level has enough room for a rec room or entertainment room, a bedroom and full bathroom with a jacuzzi tub to unwind after a long day.  Host Summer BBQs or roast marshmallows over a fire pit on your deck outside the dining room. Never worry about parking with the 2 car parking pad out back.  Conveniently located near Towson, Charles Village, Johns Hopkins, Loyola and Morgan State, the Maryland Zoo in Baltimore and Inner Harbor! Don’t miss out! Schedule your showing today!
